II. Weather and Climate Data

Goals

  • Authomatically downloading weather and climate data

Comments

  • For downloading data from Environment and Climate Change Canada (ECCC) website, we use package weathercan which can be installed directly from CRAN.

  • To downlaod data using this package, we need to know the station_id associated with the station we are interested in.

suppressMessages(library(weathercan))
